 Synergism', 'Caution is advised when brentuximab is used with potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitors (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/46957/', '', 'Pantoprazole, Tetracycline, Rabeprazole, Dexlansoprazole, Sucralfate, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Famotidine, Rifabutin, Cimetidine, Esomeprazole, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
